{"tid":1159939,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"循道衛理聯合教會：修例相當大程度損傷香港","createTime":"2019-05-18T05:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T05:53:44.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"51c91d77fd09495ab1270bd83c20aaef78d314e3","tid":1159939,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190518/s00001/dd2e95b0c3adf368728efd4d916604fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190518%2Fs00001%2Fdd2e95b0c3adf368728efd4d916604fa.jpg&h=e7b594bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天主教香港教區以外，循道衛理聯合教會香港堂昨日（17日）亦就《逃犯條例》修訂發表立場，表示在有關修訂中，中央和特區政府似無意尋求更多共識，亦無意延後或撤回，修例對香港將造成相當大損傷，港人無力感只會更深。<br />\n<br />\n另外，該教會也表示，中美貿易戰不單影響全球經濟，對中國和香港未來都造成重大損害，希望雙方能重回談判桌，達成協議和共識。"},{"pid":"68b68035f9e1aa83d2cd943caeded0de2d6d13f1","tid":1159939,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T05:53:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190518/s00001/1558155826942/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190518%2Fs00001%2F1558155826942%2F&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkFhCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=54a42526\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190518%2Fs00001%2F1558155826942%2F&h=94bdd354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190518/s00001/1558155826942/</a>"}]}